# Constraints

When making changes to this project:

## Do not change UI

- Do not modify layout, styling, navigation, or component structure
- Do not change sidebar, headers, colors, spacing, or visual design
- Only change UI when the user explicitly asks for it

## Do not change localhost

- Keep `npm run dev` as `next dev` (port 3000)
- Do not modify NEXTAUTH_URL in .env or .env.example
- Do not change dev server port, host, or dev:kill script
- Only change localhost config when the user explicitly asks for it
